Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.77,0:00:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[APEAS grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.15,0:00:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR] Hmm. This is\Nan elixir of resurrection,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.07,0:00:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and you are its vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.70,0:00:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I shall recite\Nthe incantation!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR]\NAnimus ecalp siht ot'n ruter!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[APEAS gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA rasping, grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] My name's Kage.\NAnd this is Bojji.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] Huh. Well met.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] We came here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,'cause we need you\Nto make him stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Who sent you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] Bebin gave us\Na letter of recommendation!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] Bebin?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right? How has he been?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] Doin' fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.60,0:02:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Seems a bit worse for wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.73,0:03:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] You can thank\Nyour brother for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.94,0:03:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] Huh. I see. But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] Goodness. So you're\Nthe son of none other
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,than King Bosse!\NYou must be quite talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I do apologize for\Nmy brother's cruelty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.87,0:03:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. I'm sure he was\Nlashing out in jealousy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,at the mere sight of my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure. That's\Nwhat I've heard,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but what exactly\Nis he jealous of?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He envies my strength, and my\Nnatural aptitude for leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention my modesty,\Nwork ethic, community spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and unshakeable virtue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you saw\Nthe bronze statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The people of this kingdom\Ncreated that in his honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.31,0:03:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, they made it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But then... Its face...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] Yes. The king\Ndefaced his own statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.28,0:03:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to tell you the truth,\Nhe has a complex about his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mean to boast,\Nof course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:03:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think we can agree\NI'm pretty good looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:04:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] Um. Eh. Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, you're the better\Nlooking one out of you and him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I was a child,\Npeople have naturally been
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,drawn to me, but my brother\Nwas not so fortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I would often see him\Ncrying alone in the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly, a heartbreaking sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Never mind all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The point is, you know how to\Nmake people way stronger, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You even took a totally ordinary\Nguy and made him into a king!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. That's not\Nquite how it went.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a man\Nof ordinary talents,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.28,0:04:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but there was one quality\Nthat set him apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He had courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"Courage"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The courage to keep moving\Nforward and stand tall in
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the face of adversity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The courage to put his faith\Nin others and the courage
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.96,0:04:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,never to lose his\Nfaith in himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how those around him\Nwould mock or jeer him,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,he continued to believe in\Nhis strength and his cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And without wavering,\Nstrode onward.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And before long, the people\Nfollowed in his path,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and formed a kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.23,0:05:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing I had to\Ngive that man was advice
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,on how to grow stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then if you give\NBojji some advice,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,he can get stronger, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,As my apprentice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] Uh. Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] Mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] Uh. Money, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course, money!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I need enough compensation\Nto cover my needs,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and hopefully some wants, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got your money right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.64,0:05:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid this\Nwon't be sufficient!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.02,0:05:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's everything\NBebin gave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch. Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:06:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA]\NHmm. Children's clothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and here's some kind of potion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.58,0:06:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. I'm terribly sorry, but\NI have no use for any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA]\NWh-ho-ho-hoa! Hello, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my\Nwhole life's savings!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I've really only been\Nsaving it since I took it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,from Bojji's castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So be it! I will train you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.73,0:06:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Au! [KAGE] Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Make yourselves at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Training is most effective\Nwhen one's mind is at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So, just to be clear, you're\Ngonna make Bojji into
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,a strong king?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.29,0:06:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] Hmm...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, it'll work out fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.42,0:06:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, slow down!\NYou blowin' me off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there an issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a seat, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, hold out both hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] I possess\Nan ability to see things
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that ordinary people cannot.\NOr rather, to sense them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] What is it? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No physical strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,None...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NUh... What? I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] Nor do I,\Nbut somehow, his muscles are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What about his muscles, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA]\NThis is difficult to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,However much you train,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:07:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,however hard you push yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:07:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,your body will never\Ngrow any stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.82,0:08:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] You can never be\Nan imposing, heroic figure
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.91,0:08:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,like King Bosse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What can we do?\NHow can he become stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA]\NJust as I told you, he cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He has no strength,\Nand nothing grows from nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Bojji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.06,0:08:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.77,0:08:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You've rendered your\Npayment up front, in full.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.44,0:08:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thusly, I'm obliged\Nto render service.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.65,0:08:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Though your body is weak,\Nthere is great potential in you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting to be cultivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to help you become\Nstronger than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] Woo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you! Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.25,0:08:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:08:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! This guy is\Nsomethin' else, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.55,0:09:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no "This Guy" here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The name's "Despa" and\Nthat's what you'll call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! Got it, Despa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Nicely said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.64,0:09:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then, your training\Nwill begin tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE giggles] [BOJJI] Au!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But to help grow your strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll need to replenish\Nmy own first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take the time\Nto get settled in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] Sir! [BOJJI] Au!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE grunts]\NI was gonna ask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with your face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.64,0:09:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA groans]\NThere was an altercation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A man at the bar told me\Nmy face resembled a camel's,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so I punched him, as one does.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:09:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles wheezingly]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the matter\Nproceeded in that course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like he proceeded to\Nsmack you around pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet, fool! I came through\Nin better shape
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,than my opponent by far!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.66,0:10:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I beat him black and blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not just refusing to\Nadmit you lost, right, Despa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha... Why, the nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I could hardly conceive of\Nsomeone so devoid of tact!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[blubbers]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to bed, and I urge\Nboth of you to do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,First thing tomorrow, you shall\Nbe starting on housework,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.22,0:10:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,followed promptly by training!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! Pfft! "Lost"! Pfft!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a wimp for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE sighs] Man, that's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to tell whether it's\Nday or night underground,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI] Au.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You never had to do any\Nhousecleaning at home, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.95,0:10:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can let me worry\Nabout the chores, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You focus on your\Ntraining with Despa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Au.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.89,0:11:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.19,0:11:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.42,0:11:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Au...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI] Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.99,0:12:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI slrups] Hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI slurps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] Blegh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that smell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA grunts] Blugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Au! [DESPA] That reeks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Bojji, did you\Nmake us breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Au!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.89,0:12:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[giggles] [DESPA] Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Au! Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] He cooked it whole...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,With the shell on...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Au-au-au!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it looks and\Nsmells inedible,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but he appears\Nto be enjoying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.05,0:13:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.51,0:13:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Pwah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[coughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[wheezing]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI giggling]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.45,0:13:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] Giants... Beings with\Nbodies bigger than mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.29,0:13:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Their footsteps make\Nthe earth shake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.79,0:13:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Their sneezes form\Nmighty tornados.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Their thirst drains\Nentire lakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In their hunger, they will\Ndevour what a thousand men
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,eat in a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] A moment, Kage?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.39,0:13:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you aware of the fact that\NBojji is the child of giants?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] No, I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not an easy thing to see,\Ngiven his stature.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Most giants are larger, of\Ncourse, and as you would expect,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,many times stronger\Nthan human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] Huh? Does that mean\Nhe's got some kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.66,0:14:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,dormant power inside him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid it's nothing\Nof the sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.54,0:14:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] Aw, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Put that aside for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Our concern is something\Nfar more immediate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Giants' bodies are adapted\Nto gulping down food whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,As such, their stomachs are able\Nto tolerate nearly anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,even most poisons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.89,0:14:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! It is vital that Bojji\Nbe kept out of the kitchen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, avoiding his cooking is a\Nmatter of life and death for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI] Au? [BOTH gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Then let us begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI] Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.49,0:15:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In order for anyone\Nto become stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,first, they must learn to\Nunderstand themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, to understand\Ntheir foes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But the right weapon\Ncan multiply one's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In taking up a weapon, one can\Nlearn many things about oneself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,First, you will seek out\Nthe weapon that's
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.55,0:15:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,best-suited for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kage. I would ask\Nthat you stay out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.93,0:15:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] Uh. Yeah, sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.15,0:15:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] Weapons of every\Nsize and configuration
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,have been collected here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I already have one\Nin mind that I believe
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,would greatly augment\Nyour strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I'll leave\Nfinding it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Set aside everything you've\Nbeen taught about weapons
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,as you choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:16:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI gasps]\N[TOWNSPEOPLE laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI] Mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.28,0:16:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.08,0:16:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.04,0:16:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.34,0:16:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No sooner did you lay eyes\Non it than you recognized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,With that at your side,\Nyou will be unmatched.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.39,0:16:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall teach you the knowledge\Nand techniques to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.48,0:16:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NThey've been at it for a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.44,0:16:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Bojji's been training with Despa\Nall day, from morning to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My thanks to you, Kage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI] Au...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.29,0:17:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighing]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] And at the end,\Nhe's always so exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that he pretty much passes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Every single day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why's Bojji gotta train\Nbehind closed doors?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] Mm. He just needs\Ntime to ponder and brood
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.56,0:17:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and polish his\Nskills by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That solitude will be\Nthe spice of his success.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.94,0:17:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're worried... he's losing\Nheart, please encourage him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but you mustn't ask him\Nabout his training.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. You got it, Despa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.20,0:17:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA]\NThank you for the fine meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] Hmm. Although,\Nmore than anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspect he just doesn't\Nwant to spoil the surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight... Bojji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI] Au! Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Au! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[screeching]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[screeches]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[yawns]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.36,0:19:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] Welcome back!\NI got breakfast ready for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI] Au!\N[DESPA] Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it looks as\Ndelicious as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:19:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.75,0:20:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] Ahm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.38,0:20:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL laugh]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.93,0:20:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] Right. Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.97,0:20:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, Bojji! Hang tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.72,0:20:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Au!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[clanging]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[boom] Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys! What the heck's\Ngoin' on in there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We're training.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that gigantic\Nrumbling I just heard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] Nothing to concern\Nyourself with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] Uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.04,0:20:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.17,0:20:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So once more... I have given\Nmy son as my sacrifice.
